    background-color: #E8F5FD;

      <li class="embed-link js-actionEmbedTweet" data-nav="embed_tweet">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Embed Tweet</button>
      </li>
  </ul>
</div>

</div>

  </div>

      </div>

      

      


      
        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">In evidence to the Brexit Committee <a href="/DavidDavisMP" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="2797521996"><s>@</s><b>DavidDavisMP</b></a> ridiculed the useless Bank of England forecasts on the consequences of a vote to leave. Too polite to say they were politically motivated.</p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Bonsoir, old thing, cheer-i-o, chin, chin,

      </li>
  </ul>
</div>

      <li class="copy-link-to-tweet js-actionCopyLinkToTweet">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Copy link to Tweet</button>
      </li>
      <li class="embed-link js-actionEmbedTweet" data-nav="embed_tweet">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Embed Tweet</button>

  </ul>
